Description: Simple GTK3-based translator for selected text
 A simple and efficient translation application that translates selected text
 instantly. Built with GTK3 and Python, it provides seamless translation
 without interrupting your workflow.
 .
 Features:
  - Instant translation of selected text
  - Automatic text selection monitoring
  - Dictionary lookup functionality
  - Smart cursor-relative window positioning
  - Clean GTK3 interface with dynamic layouts
  - Simple and intuitive to use
 .
 SelectTranslate monitors clipboard changes and provides instant translation
 for any selected text, positioning the translation window near the cursor
 for optimal workflow integration.